# Day6 Final Reflection

The most important realization today is:

```text
Engineering work is not only writing code.

Engineering work also includes:

finding code,
understanding structure,
tracking changes,
and organizing information.
```

Or more structurally:

```text
repository
→ search
→ inspection
→ understanding
→ modification
→ version control
```

This workflow scales from small C++ exercises to larger AI and spacecraft projects.

## Search Before Modify

Engineering workflow:

Locate
→ Read
→ Understand
→ Modify
→ Verify

Do not modify code before understanding where it is used.

